        "subject": "LU-19469 utils: set/clear LUSTRE_SPARSE_FL on a regular file",
        "message": "LU-19469 utils: set/clear LUSTRE_SPARSE_FL on a regular file\n\nThis patch adds a new LUSTRE_SPARSE_FL to indicate that the file\nmarked with this flag is sparse.\nAdd a command to set/clear the flag:\n\t$LFS chattr [+|-s] [+|-sparse] $FILE ...\nAdd a command to display the FSFLAGS on a file:\n\t$FLS lsattr $FILE...\n\nAdd sanity/test_855g to test this flag.\n\nChange-Id: Ibd0d2965802f9f711b9f54adbccca919e2c9965c\nSigned-off-by: Yingjin Qian <qian@ddn.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
